  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators' aim is to study the effect of cycling off criteria during pressure support
      ventilation in COPD patients at two levels of PEEP and PSV.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study two levels of cycling off criteria at two levels of PEEP and PSV were tested in
      term of gas exchange, respiratory mechanics, work of breathing and patient comfort.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
